## 🧮 Why Not MD5?

| Property | MD5 | SHA-256 |
|---|---|---|
| Output size | 128 bits | 256 bits |
| Collision attacks | ✅ Known collisions exist | ❌ No known collisions |
| Speed | Faster | Fast enough |
| Security status | **BROKEN** — don't use | Industry standard |
| Example attack | Two PDFs with same MD5 hash possible | Computationally infeasible |

DocuGuard includes MD5 only for informational/legacy display — never for security decisions.

