## 📈 Performance Characteristics

```
File: 10 MB PDF
  SHA-256:    ~15ms
  SHA3-256:   ~20ms  
  HMAC-SHA256: ~16ms
  Total:       ~51ms — nearly instant!

File: 100 MB video
  SHA-256:    ~150ms
  Total:       ~0.5 seconds — still fast!
```

DocuGuard can process documents of any size — hash computation scales linearly with file size.
